	LairMUD V1.0  - Docs!

	Okay, these are going to be short and simple. LairMUD is
a 1 or 2 player text based fantasy adventure. After playing several
MUDs (Multi-User Dungeons) on Internet, I decided I could make one
on the Amiga that two people could play together. If you want to
play with another player (which is reccomended) the  person will
need a modem to call you on. This game supports speeds 1200-19200BPS.
This game should work on ALL Amigas, however, the only Amiga I have
tested this on is my Amiga 500 with 512K Chip and 2.5K RAM with
OS 2.04. Its written in GFA-BASIC 3.52, and runs very fast with no
lag whatsoever. The program is FREEWARE, which means, its free to
upload anywhere or send it to anyone you like. Im not asking for
donations for this program or anything. I WILL be updating it a lot
nd it will be posted on the internet whenever a new version is
released, so it should spread around fairly quickly. If you have any
questions or comments you can mail me at  dongho@cs.wisc.edu on the
Internet. Hope you enjoy it.

